<HEADLINE> Spanish Davis Cup Squad Named </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MADRID, March 24 (Xinhua) -- Carlos Moya, Alberto Costa, Javier
Sanchez and Francis Roig will line up for Spain at next month's
Davis Cup quarter-final tie against Italy.
</P>
<P>
Moya and Costa will contest the singles. Meanwhile, Sanchez
will team up with Roig, who will be making his Davis Cup debut,
for the doubles rubber in the best-of-five encounter slated for
April 4-6 in Pesaro, Italy's Adriatic coast. 
</P>
