<TEXT>
<P>
VIENNA, March 24 (Xinhua) -- The average price of OPEC crude
oil was up 0.34 U.S. dollars to 18.94 dollars per barrel last
week, the Vienna-based OPEC Secretariat said today.
</P>
<P>
