distributed 7,641 tones of maize to nine striken regions
concerned following applications of the need of emegency food
reach to his ministry.
</P>
<P>
He said that the government has also issued 500 tons of maize
seeds to facilitate seven regions hit by drought.
</P>
<P>
The minister further said the government has set aside some
money to be used in getting and distributing sweet potatoes seeds
from Mbeya region and cassava seeds from Mtwara to the affected
areas.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, the minister was very much pleased with the rains
which was reported to feature almost in every region over the
past two days. He said he hoped that the situation will be at
normal. 
</P>
