<HEADLINE> Hungary Hails Result of Helsinki Summit </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUDAPEST, March 25 (Xinhua) -- The Hungarian Foreign Ministry
said today last week's U.S.-Russian summit in Helsinki gave
grounds for cautious optimism.
</P>
