<HEADLINE> Chinese, US Vice-Presidents Meet </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 25 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Vice-President Rong Yiren
said here today that the common interests between China and the
United States far exceed their differences and that the two
countries should establish healthy and stable relations with an
eye to the 21st century.
