<P>
ANKARA, March 25 (Xinhua) -- Azerbaijani President Geidar
Aliyev will pay a three-day official visit to Turkey starting on
April 8 to enhance the cooperation between the two countries,
local newspaper Daily News reported today.
</P>
<P>
