<HEADLINE> Sampras Advances at Lipton Championships </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, March 24 (Xinhua) -- Top seed Pete Sampras showed
winning form at the Lipton Championships Monday by winning a 6-3,
7-6, (7-3) third-round victory over 36th-ranked Francisco Clavet
of Spain.
</P>
