<HEADLINE> Marseille President Pledges Future to Club </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, March 24 (Xinhua) -- Marseille president Robert
Louis-Dreyfus vowed on Monday to pour money into the French club
next season and dismissed the rumours that he would be quitting.
